[Patient] What exercises can I do safely in my neighborhood?
[Educator] You can try indoor exercises like yoga or bodyweight workouts at home. 
[Patient] But I prefer outdoor activities. Any suggestions for safe places?
[Educator] Look for community centers, gyms, or local parks with supervised exercise options. 
[Patient] My friends are not into exercise. What should I do?
[Educator] Try joining group fitness classes or asking family to accompany you for support. 
[Patient] Will exercise really help my heart failure symptoms?
[Educator] Regular exercise can improve heart health, reduce complications, and improve quality of life.